      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. i want to make it even stronger though. can you add a section that addresses the 'meritocracy' argument? like, how can i frame the idea that wealth is earned through hard work as being basically an invalid excuse for why people stay stuck in these racial wealth gaps? i want to show why that mindset is actually part of the problem.",
